      <title>俄罗斯将《华尔街日报》记者告上法庭，指控其从事间谍活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/russia-sends-wsj-reporter-s-case-to-court-accuses-him-of-spying</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总检察长办公室正式将入狱的《华尔街日报》记者埃文·格什科维奇的案件送交法庭，指控他“按照中央情报局的指示”从事间谍活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/russia-sends-wsj-reporter-s-case-to-court-accuses-him-of-spying</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 13:23:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西财政部长面临任期内最艰难时刻，光芒黯淡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/brazil-finance-chief-s-star-fades-as-he-faces-worst-moment-of-tenure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[18 个月以来，巴西财政部长费尔南多·阿达德 (Fernando Haddad) 一直在总统希望花钱和投资者要求财政纪律之间走钢丝，现在他开始失去平衡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/brazil-finance-chief-s-star-fades-as-he-faces-worst-moment-of-tenure</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国首次对俄罗斯影子船队油轮实施制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/uk-imposes-first-sanctions-on-russia-s-shadow-fleet-oil-tankers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国宣布对俄罗斯实施广泛制裁，包括首次试图取缔运输克里姆林宫石油的影子油轮船队和一家位于莫斯科的重要保险公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/uk-imposes-first-sanctions-on-russia-s-shadow-fleet-oil-tankers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 11:48:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国考虑增加 2024 年预算以弥补 110 亿欧元的缺口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/germany-mulls-extra-2024-budget-to-plug-11-billion-shortfall</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，德国财政部正在考虑今年的补充预算，额外借款高达 110 亿欧元（119 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/germany-mulls-extra-2024-budget-to-plug-11-billion-shortfall</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 11:38:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国大选关键时刻，斯塔默提出工党增长计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/starmer-sets-out-labour-s-growth-plan-in-key-uk-election-moment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[工党领袖基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 阐述了该党以经济增长和安全为重点的政府计划，这对于 7 月 4 日英国大选前英国首相候选人来说是一个关键时刻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/starmer-sets-out-labour-s-growth-plan-in-key-uk-election-moment</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 10:35:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>道奇称加拿大需要“激光聚焦”生产力战略</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/canada-needs-laser-focused-productivity-strategy-dodge-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大央行前行长戴维·道奇 (David Dodge) 共同撰写的一份新报告指出，加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多的政府及其省级同行必须“全神贯注”地提高加拿大经济的生产能力，否则可能进一步落后于其他国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/canada-needs-laser-focused-productivity-strategy-dodge-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 10:31:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国和欧洲如何争取俄罗斯资产交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/g7-deal-on-russia-assets-and-ukraine-funding-highlights-allies-differences</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自弗拉基米尔·普京入侵乌克兰初期以来，其央行约有 3000 亿美元的资金一直在比利时等地的账户中赚取收入。]]></description>
